results.title: Ultimate Spider-Man (2000) #68
results.description: SUPERSTARS PART 3 Johnny Storm still doesn't have a high school diploma. And where does the young New Yorker enroll? Why none other than a certain Queens high school that also has one Peter Parker, Spider-Man as a student!

results.title: Ultimate Spider-Man (2000) #69
results.description: SUPERSTARS PART 4 Johnny Storm just wants to fit in. But it's hard to fit in when you're consumed entirely by flames! The cat's out of the bag after Johnny's big reveal and Peter Parker is on damage control!
